{"tid":1858643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"成都5.1級地震","createTime":"2020-02-02T23:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T23:23:45.000Z","uid":326897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f20954e455afc53a1e88f68c656e07dda3cd6d8","tid":1858643,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T23:00:39.000Z","msg":"成都清白江區5.1級地震 成都提前8秒接獲預警<br />\n2020-02-03 HKT 04:20<br />\n <br />\n四川成都市清白江區發生5.1級地震，暫時未收到傷亡報告。<br />\n<br />\n中國地震台網測定，地震在凌晨零時05分發生，震源深度21公里。金堂縣一名市民說，地震搖了十幾秒，家中震感明顯，床劇烈晃動。另外，成都、樂山、綿陽、德陽等地，震感強烈。<br />\n<br />\n地震後，四川省應急管理廳緊急啟動三級響應，派出工作組前往震央核查災情，指導抗震救援工作。<br />\n<br />\n中新社報道，當局建立的地震預警網成功預警這次地震，向成都市提前8秒發出預警。一些位於震央附近的手機、電視等發出預警提示。<br />\n<br />\n青白江區位於成都市東北部，距成都主城區25公里，是四川省重要的冶金、建材和機械製造基地，也是中國西部最大的鐵路物流樞紐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506261-20200203.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506261-20200203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=e3888109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506261-20200203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8f4cddf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506261-20200203.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n天滅支那，雜帝敗了，<br />\n柒婆壞了，香港勝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828b89501a241ad277ea3ef8ae598634152ae101","tid":1858643,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T23:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H66EJPN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH66EJPN.png&h=6689477a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3369bfa67cb90bdd137d926062023fbc7556dbe","tid":1858643,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T23:23:45.000Z","msg":"old news"}]}